"Plugin %s was installed but the main plugin file could not be found. The "
"installation may be incomplete or the plugin structure is invalid."
msgstr ""
"افزونه %s نصب شد اما فایل اصلی افزونه یافت نشد. نصب ممکن است ناقص باشد یا "
"ساختار افزونه نامعتبر باشد."

#. translators: %s is the plugin slug.
#: inc/lib/onboarding/classes/class-astra-sites-install-plugin.php:169
